text: Mill Valley is a city of Marin County in the state of California, United States. It is about north of San Francisco by way of the Golden Gate Bridge. The population was 14,231 at the 2020 census. Actress and comedian, Eve Arden was born there in 1908. ==References== Category:1900s establishments in California Category:1900 establishments in the United States Category:Cities in California Category:Settlements in Marin County, California Category:Cities in the San Francisco Bay Area
